RC TRANSMITTER UNIT

Hardware:
1. Arduino Nano (Atmega 328)
2. RF Link transmitter (433 MHz)
3. 3-axis Accelerometer (ADXL330)
4. 8x LEDS and 8x 220 Ohm rezistors
5. 3x switches
6. 9V Battery

  TX unit                 Arduino Nano                  ADXL 330
 ---------         ----------------------------      --------------
 |   GND |---------| GND                   A7 |------| X axis     |
 |   VCC |---------| +5V                   A6 |------| Y axis     |
 |   DATA|---------| D13                  +5V |------| +5V        |
 |   ANT |----     |                      GND |------| GND        |
 ---------   |     |                          |      --------------
             |     |                          |
   antenna - o     |                          |
                   |                          |   R1-R8 LED1-LED8
    battery + o----| VCC                   D4 |---|===|---|<|-----|
    battery - o----| GND                   D5 |---|===|---|<|-----|
                   |                       D6 |---|===|---|<|-----|
      Switches     |                       D8 |---|===|---|<|-----|
   ----/ ----------| A0                    D9 |---|===|---|<|-----|
   |---/ ----------| D2                    D10|---|===|---|<|-----|
   |---/ ----------| D3                    D11|---|===|---|<|-----|
   |               |                       D12|---|===|---|<|-----|
   o               |                          |                   |
  GND              |                          |                   |
                   ----------------------------                   o
                                                                 GND

RC RECEIVER UNIT

Hardware:
1. Arduino Uno (Atmega 328)
2. RF Link receiver module (433 MHz)
3. Motor shield (LXXX)
4. 2 DC 5V motors
5. Chassis
6. 6V battery
7. 8x LEDS and 8x 220 Ohm rezistors
8. 2x blue LEDs and 2x 220 Ohm rezistors

